dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Fond du Lac County, WI 2017
dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents hydrography for Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin in 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Fond_du_Lac_Hydro_2017.gdb.[Open water features were generated from the digital orthophotography obtained in 2000. All work was done by Ayers Associates.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For complete metadata documentation and online dataset download, please visit http://www.fdlco.wi.gov/departments/departments-f-m/land-information/data-download.This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2017. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2016. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2017.
